label: ABCD_tP8_129_c_b_a_c-001
title: AsCuSiZr Structure
comments:
This is the parent structure for the iron-pnictide superconductors. 
 This structure has the same space group and Wyckoff positions as \href{current_web_home_dir/ABCD_tP8_129_b_c_a_c-001}{LaOAgS}, but there is a substantial difference in the $c/a$ ratio leading to different bonding between the layers.
